========================
 Short URL (surl)
========================

Remember NOT TO MAKE IT PUBLIC IN ANY WAY SHAPE OR FORM. THe spammers will kill you.

usertag/surl.am
usertag/surl.tag
dbconf/mysql/surl.mysql
pages/query/surl_create.html

in httpd config (5 or more uppercase characters):
	RewriteRule ^/([A-Z0-9][A-Z0-9][A-Z0-9][A-Z0-9][A-Z0-9][A-Z0-9]*)$ /cgi-bin/public/surl/$1 [L,NS,PT]

Add a link to your Miscellaneous page menu, if you want. Be sure to include the "pwd=password" in the form part.

